restaurant-name: 新泰城泰雲小館 (高雄大順店)
restaurant-name-pinyin: Xīn tài chéng tài yún xiǎoguǎn (gāoxióng dà shùn diàn)
dish-description: 酥脆外皮鮮甜內餡，搭配沾醬真是一大享受。(此描述僅供參考)
dish-description-pinyin: Sūcuì wàipí xiān tián nèi xiàn, dāpèi zhān jiàng zhēnshi yī dà xiǎngshòu.(Cǐ miáoshù jǐn gōng cānkǎo)
dish-description-english: Crispy on the outside and sweet on the inside, it's a treat to pair with dipping sauce. (This description is for reference only)
